headline: 5 Revealing Analyst Questions From Tractor Supply’s Q1 Earnings Call
summary: Tractor Supply’s first quarter 2025 performance was shaped by delayed spring weather and persistent pressure in big-ticket seasonal categories. Management pointed to robust customer transactions and growth in consumable, usable, and edible categories, but noted that adverse weather conditions, especially in southern markets, held back overall sales.
